{"type": "article", "id": 33157, "title": "KENZO 与 H&M 合作系列完整公开，以及，推荐一辆车 | 浮华日报", "description": "我们为你挑选了今天最重要和最好看的时尚新闻。", "date": "2016-10-11T02:35:23Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 19652, "name": "Line Friends"}, {"id": 466, "name": "LVMH"}, {"id": 1060, "name": "H&M"}, {"id": 2034, "name": "Dior"}, {"id": 2040, "name": "KENZO"}, {"id": 8634, "name": "Supreme"}, {"id": 10763, "name": "CLOT"}, {"id": 30020, "name": "Brompton"}, {"id": 32840, "name": "Honest"}, {"id": 33794, "name": "Aquascutum"}, {"id": 17411, "name": "陈冠希"}, {"id": 32842, "name": "Jessica Alba"}], "category": 19, "column": 8, "author": 699895, "comment_count": 7, "praise_count": 71, "image": "img/article/article_show/20161011080456PO5ezqM8hFAnUWby.jpg", "contents": "<h3>一些重要的新闻：</h3><p><a href=\"http://wwd.com/beauty-industry-news/financial/jessica-albas-honest-beauty-expands-plans-canada-launch-10658233/\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>Honest 寻求扩张，下一个市场是加拿大</b></a> | 作为好莱坞明星创业的优秀案例，美妆品牌 Honest 早已实现了 1000 万美元的销售额，此前曾传出联合利华要收购 Honest 的消息。近日，据 Honest 的市场总监 Chris Throne 所称，Honest 将进军加拿大市场。&nbsp;</p><p><a href=\"https://techcrunch.com/2016/10/04/spains-sunglasses-startup-hawkers-nabs-56m-to-take-on-the-ray-bans-of-the-world/\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>西班牙互联网眼镜品牌 Hawkers 获 5000 万欧元融资</b></a> | 西班牙公司 Saldum Ventures 融资了 5000 万欧元，想要打造一个数字化的全新太阳镜公司 Hawkers 。Hawkers 创办于 2 年前，现在年销售额约为 7000 万欧元。它计划利用这笔融资继续在欧洲扩张，开设更多的概念实体店。&nbsp;</p><p><a href=\"http://wwd.com/business-news/forecasts-analysis/consumers-plan-to-spend-an-average-of-636-on-holiday-related-expenses-npd-finds-10659333/\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>年底假日期间，预计消费者平均消费 636 美元用于假日相关支出</b></a> | 市场调研机构 NPD 的报告指出，今年年底，消费者计划平均消费 636 美元用于假日相关支出，这个数字相比去年上涨了 3%。</p><p class=\"\"><a href=\"https://www.businessoffashion.com/articles/news-analysis/lvmh-sales-beat-estimates-on-fashion-and-leather-goods\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>LVMH 集团第三季度营收超预期</b></a> | 世界最大的奢侈品集团 LVMH 第三季度收益超预期，销售额增长至 91.4 亿欧元，超过了此前分析师预测的 89.2 亿欧元。据 LVMH 所称，即使欧洲受恐怖袭击影响，旅游奢侈品消费减少，得益于表现良好的亚洲和美国地区，集团仍然实现了不错的增长。&nbsp;</p><h3>一些值得一看的：</h3><p><a href=\"http://hypebeast.cn/2016/10/kenzo-x-hm-2016-fall-winter-lookbook\" rel=\"nofollow\">KENZO 与 H&amp;M 合作系列</a>完整公开。该系列以丛林迷彩为主题，充满了夸张的图案和张扬的色彩，具有很强的视觉冲击（杀伤）力。&nbsp;</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201610110907178EULIAYBx23srvWR.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161011090730hJTC8pcMfnOAaEZN.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161011090730LcOu0gBAi5H3f8VN.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161011090730JLOfysuh8FETMR96.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161011090744TtMP5ZvbgWDJ07cE.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161011092545kb0LaYu5rwPKVS8z.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p>Line Friends 与英国经典折叠单车品牌 Brompton 合作，推出名为 <a href=\"http://hypebeast.cn/2016/10/line-firends-launch-limited-edition-brompton\" rel=\"nofollow\">Made For Brown </a>的限量版折叠单车。Brown 熊打扮成英国绅士，出现在 Brompton 上。这款单车限量发售 50 架，现已开售。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201610110907554A0tSJxKUVPTLb2y.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666992\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201610110908107Mpdko2FYuQtUCzy.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201610110908195JLh0KlrIWqSwaiu.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161011090835XJlmh4uiAUvnxb3G.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666992\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161011090844h2wZBYUOEWbg4o9C.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666992\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161011090856fbEKztAFGLhj37vJ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666992\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201610110909295NWc2HkPTJ7dhmX6.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666016\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161011090942oOtwXqLzYjdaHuJb.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666992\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p class=\"\"><a href=\"http://hypebeast.cn/2016/10/supreme-x-aquascutum-2016-fw-collection\" rel=\"nofollow\">Supreme 与英国经典品牌 Aquascutum 合作</a>，重现了 Aquascutum 于 1976 年首度登场的经典格纹 Club Check，推出了令人惊喜的 2016 秋冬系列。<span style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</span></p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161011091049BVdgb3GXwCK4qtaA.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161011091101hBDC567gk0w1qV9S.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161011091110eawZS9lhOQFqp2rc.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161011091121g5MmN9evCDGFi34S.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161011091141HGcPtLDl3AwyUSvs.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><p>Dior 今年的<a href=\"http://popbee.com/beauty/make-up/dior-splendor-holiday-2016-collection/\" rel=\"nofollow\">圣诞限定彩妆</a>还挺好看的，它主打粉红色调，还融入了高级定制工坊的刺绣元素。&nbsp;</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161011092649HBcDfu0dm1ilROTp.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161011092659I91CBKZFldqJtM7A.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667480\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161011092708GjVYb4dnBJ9u2OwR.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161011092716zGT9JFkanXm4ZPtr.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667480\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p>CLOT 与艺术家 Eric Elms 推出<a href=\"http://hypebeast.cn/2016/10/clot-x-eric-elms\" rel=\"nofollow\">联名系列</a>，该系列包括了一系列 Tee 及卫衣，还有不少 Eric Elms 为 CLOT 设计的富有玩味的图案。&nbsp;</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201610110928381nDt0TGlkAYB3hHK.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161011092824zmUDdu6f0pkibQc2.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161011092813q7Qa8mwWkyUBM09e.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161011092806yxdBD7nkmzjTZu3Q.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201610110927468UgDQXoZdphAnSMO.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161011092755N9EkpBIoyeLfO6w4.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p class=\"\"><br></p>"}